            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>L3Harris Technologies <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20494250-l3harris-technologies-reports-strong-first-quarter-2026-results\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LHX\" title=\"L3Harris Technologies, Inc.\">LHX</a></span>): Q1 GAAP EPS of $2.72 <span> beats by $0.20</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $5.7B (+11.8% Y/Y) <span> beats by $290M</span>.</li>\n<li>Orders of $7.8 billion; book-to-bill of 1.4x increases backlog to new record $40.7 billion</li>\n<li>Revenue of $5.7 billion, up 12%, and 15% organically*</li>\n<li>Operating margin of 11.4% up 120 bps; Segment operating margin of 15.7% up 10 bps</li>\n<li>GAAP diluted EPS of $2.72, up 33%</li>\n<li>Guidance: Revenue: <span>$23B - $23.5B (vs. consensus of $23.44B; Diluted EPS: $11.40 - $11.60 (Prior: $11.30 - $11.50) (consensus at $11.67)</span><span> </span><div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<span class=\"sa-table-scroll-wrapper sa-hide-scrollbar\"><span data-intersection-boundary=\"start\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-start\"></span><div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<span class=\"sa-table-scroll-wrapper sa-hide-scrollbar\"><span data-intersection-boundary=\"start\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-start\"></span><table data-should-enlarge=\"true\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> </td></tr></tbody></table>\n<span data-intersection-boundary=\"end\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-end\"></span></span><button class=\"sa-table-enlarge-button\" type=\"button\">Click to enlarge</button>\n</div>\n<span data-intersection-boundary=\"end\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-end\"></span></span><button class=\"sa-table-enlarge-button\" type=\"button\">Click to enlarge</button>\n</div>\n<span></span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
