            "id": "4582596",
            "title": "Trump has surprisingly mild reaction to Powell staying at Fed",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\">President Donald Trump appeared to brush off Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell’s decision to remain on the Board of Governors until the investigation into the Fed’s building renovation is completed.</p>\n<p>At his post-FOMC press conference, Powell said he would stay on for a period “to be determined,” citing the administration’s actions in launching a criminal probe and what he described as a threat to the Fed’s independence.</p>\n<p>Trump responded in a social media post: “Jerome ‘Too Late’ Powell wants to stay at the Fed because he can’t get a job anywhere else — nobody wants him.”</p>\n<p> </p>\n<figure class=\"regular-img-figure\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span><img alt=\"Trump on Powell\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/4a09ba05a7dd22e2b828e64d97a36023.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox\" data-source=\"Truth Social\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"306\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1023px) calc(100vw - 180px), 552px\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/4a09ba05a7dd22e2b828e64d97a36023.png?io=w640\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/4a09ba05a7dd22e2b828e64d97a36023.png?io=w750 750w,https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/4a09ba05a7dd22e2b828e64d97a36023.png?io=w640 640w,https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/4a09ba05a7dd22e2b828e64d97a36023.png?io=w480 480w,https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/4a09ba05a7dd22e2b828e64d97a36023.png?io=w320 320w,https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/4a09ba05a7dd22e2b828e64d97a36023.png?io=w240 240w\" width=\"900\"/></span><figcaption class=\"overlay-title\"><p class=\"item-caption\"><span class=\"item-source\">Truth Social</span></p></figcaption></figure><p> </p>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\">